<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Day 3: Master Your Content Strategy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .tip-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .content-type {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Day 3: Master Your Content Strategy</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name %>,</h2>

            <p>You're making great progress! Today, let's talk about building a winning LinkedIn content strategy.</p>

            <p><strong>The 4 Content Types That Drive Engagement:</strong></p>

            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <span class="content-type">üìñ Story Posts</span>
                <span class="content-type">Insight Shares</span>
                <span class="content-type">‚ùì Question Posts</span>
                <span class="content-type">üìã List Posts</span>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-box">
                <strong style="color: #2e7d32;">The 3-2-1 Strategy:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #2e7d32;">Post 3 times per week: 2 value-driven posts + 1
                    engagement post. This balance builds authority while fostering community.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Pro Tips for Higher Engagement:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Post timing:</strong> Early morning (7-9 AM) or lunch hours (12-1 PM)</li>
                <li><strong>Length:</strong> 150-300 words for maximum readability</li>
                <li><strong>Hashtags:</strong> Use 3-5 relevant hashtags</li>
                <li><strong>Call-to-action:</strong> Always end with a question or invitation</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%=  %>/dashboard/content-ideas"
                    class="cta-button">
                    Get Content Ideas ‚Üí
                </a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Coming up on Day 5:</strong><br>
                We'll unlock advanced features like comment generators and profile analysis!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Keep crushing it!<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>